## Features Implemented

### 1. Immersive Landing Page ([app/page.js](file:///c:/Users/kouki/.gemini/hifuu-kou-club/app/page.js))
- **Hero Animation**: A dramatic entry sequence with fading curtains and glitch-in typography.
- **Visuals**: A "Washi" (Japanese paper) noise texture overlay on a deep charcoal background (`#1a1a1a`), accented with Hakurei Red (`#E60033`).
- **Atmosphere**: Floating "Sakura" particles created with Framer Motion to give a sense of depth and flow.

### 2. Navigation ([components/Navigation.js](file:///c:/Users/kouki/.gemini/hifuu-kou-club/components/Navigation.js))
- **Persistent Layout**: A top navigation bar that slides in after the intro.
- **Style**: Mimics a Shinto "Ofuda" or sealing strip with vertical text elements.
- **Links**: Home, News, Diary, Characters.

### 3. News Section ([app/news/page.js](file:///c:/Users/kouki/.gemini/hifuu-kou-club/app/news/page.js))
- **Design**: "Ema" (wooden plaque) style cards.
- **Animation**: Staggered entry for each news item.
- **Data**: Loaded from [data/news.json](file:///c:/Users/kouki/.gemini/hifuu-kou-club/data/news.json).

### 4. Diary / DevLog ([app/diary/page.js](file:///c:/Users/kouki/.gemini/hifuu-kou-club/app/diary/page.js))
- **Design**: A vertical timeline on a scroll-like background.
- **Features**: Includes a "Video Progress" bar to visualize production status.
- **Data**: Loaded from [data/diary.json](file:///c:/Users/kouki/.gemini/hifuu-kou-club/data/diary.json).

### 5. Character Introduction ([components/CharacterSection.js](file:///c:/Users/kouki/.gemini/hifuu-kou-club/components/CharacterSection.js))
